"As an Assistant Commercial Manager, you will be part of the wider W2BC Project team delivering works for the Transpennine Route Upgrade between Huddersfield and Stalybridge. You'll have an interesting and varied role, providing commercial support as required in accordance with established Network Rail policy. Day-to-day, you'll operate effectively in multi-disciplined teams, supporting both the Commercial Manager and project team. You will assist the Commercial Manager in pre-contract activities and evaluating and agreeing the value of payments and variations for a variety of works throughout the Route."